Subject Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan - Agreement for the Promotion and Protection of Investments Ratification
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to ratify, on behalf of Canada, the AGREEMENT between Canada and the Hashemite Kingdom of JORDAN for the Promotion and Protection of Investments to provide stronger protection for Canadian investors and their investments in Jordan.
